standard:
  commercialize_multitenant_saas:
    proposal_name: commercialize_multitenant_saas
    model: tencent/hy3:free
    objective: 'Re-platform PlugBoot from a single-user local YAML workspace into a multi-tenant B2B SaaS where independent customers log in, see a private dashboard, and run the PlugBoot automation engine per-tenant. Backend automation = self-hosted n8n; master database = Supabase. This mission is the PLANNING phase only: produce the architecture, schema, and workflow blueprints before any code is written.'
    priority: HIGH
    state:
      class: PLANNING
      progress: pending
    rounds: 0
    goals:
      repo_clone: Clone this PlugBoot workspace into a new plugboot-saas folder ON THE DESKTOP (C:\Users\BAB AL SAFA\Desktop\plugboot-saas), do all re-platforming work there, then push to https://github.com/Auto-Skiller/plugboot-saas. Source of truth for the SaaS move lives in that repo, not this one.
      auth_isolation: Define and stand up the tenant isolation + authentication foundation (Supabase Auth, tenants/users/orgs tables, Row-Level Security) so one customer can never read another's data.
      data_model: Convert the 8 YAML schemas into a Supabase Postgres schema using JSONB for nested structures, preserving the entity / inbox / mission model.
      replatform_sync: Re-point the inbox->analyse->gateway sync logic from local disk to n8n workflows that operate on Supabase (keep the logic, change the storage).
      tenant_dashboard: Re-skin the existing Alpine dashboard to read/write via an authenticated API gateway; add org switcher + automated tenant provisioning.
      commercial: Define plans/tiers, usage metering, and Stripe billing for the per-customer deploy model.
    tasks:
      clone_to_plugboot_saas:
        progress: pending
        owner: agent
        detail: git clone this workspace into plugboot-saas ON THE DESKTOP (C:\Users\BAB AL SAFA\Desktop\plugboot-saas), build the multi-tenant re-platform there, and push to https://github.com/Auto-Skiller/plugboot-saas. All subsequent tasks execute against that repo.
      draft_supabase_schema:
        progress: pending
        owner: agent
        detail: Produce SQL DDL for tenants, users, orgs, entities, inbox, missions, toolboxes tables with tenant_id + RLS policies, derived from the 8 schemas.
      sketch_n8n_workflows:
        progress: pending
        owner: agent
        detail: Export n8n workflow JSON for tenant provisioning + inbox-sync that runs the same detect/gap/route logic against Supabase.
      define_isolation_model:
        progress: pending
        owner: agent
        detail: Decide isolated-per-tenant containers vs shared-engine-scoped-data; recommend the safer model for B2B customer-data handling.
      write_technical_brief:
        progress: pending
        owner: agent
        detail: 'One-page non-technical stakeholder brief: the move, phases, timeline, and risks.'
