    rounds: 0
    goals:
      repo_clone: Clone this PlugBoot workspace into a new plugboot-hhmed folder ON THE DESKTOP (C:\Users\BAB AL SAFA\Desktop\plugboot-hhmed), do the project seeding there, then push to https://github.com/Auto-Skiller/plugboot-hhmed.
      seed_projects: Add some real projects into the plugboot-hhmed workspace (new project folders with board/runtime/missions/toolboxes/inbox entities) so the repo demonstrates multi-project usage.
